    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems so messy when you actually try to draw it out. like, when you have all those different levels and all the lines are branching off to different nodes, it gets really hard to track the hierarchy. is there a way to make the branching more consistent so it doesn't look like a tangled mess?",
